BT /F2 11.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 687.00 Tm (1. Frontend - frontend/run.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 672.00 Tm (A Streamlit chat interface that renders the conversation, calls the backend's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 657.50 Tm (invoke_agent\(\), and persists both chat_context and sly_data in session state so) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 643.00 Tm (identity and current client are remembered across turns.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 617.50 Tm (2. Backend - backend/run.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 602.50 Tm (A thin module that bootstraps env vars \(AGENT_MANIFEST_FILE, AGENT_TOOL_PATH,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 588.00 Tm (PYTHONPATH\), loads .env, and exposes invoke_agent\(agent_name, user_text, sly_data,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 573.50 Tm (chat_context\) using neuro-san's in-process DirectAgentSessionFactory.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 548.00 Tm (3. Agent Registry - backend/registries/) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 524.00 Tm (File                       Purpose                                                      ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 512.95 Tm (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 502.33 Tm (manifest.hocon             Lists the active agent network                               ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 491.28 Tm (standards_concierge.hocon  Defines the 29 agents/tools and their instructions           ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 480.23 Tm (aaosa.hocon                AAOSA substitution variables \(aaosa_instructions, aaosa_call\)) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 469.18 Tm (llm_config.hocon           Shared LLM configuration \(Anthropic claude-sonnet\)           ) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 441.12 Tm (4. Multi-Agent Network - standards_concierge.hocon) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 426.12 Tm (Three genuine routing levels \(client, team, topic\) plus four deterministic coded tools.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 411.62 Tm (Team depth is uneven by design \(Banking A-D ... Telecom A\) so routing is dynamic.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 386.12 Tm (5. CodedTools - backend/coded_tools/standards_concierge/) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 362.12 Tm (Tool                      Role                                                                        ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 351.42 Tm (------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 341.12 Tm (EmployeeDirectory         Maps a developer's name to the one client+team they may access              ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 330.42 Tm (ClientResolver            Resolves a repo/project to its client and remembers it in sly_data          ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 319.71 Tm (ScopedStandardsRetriever  Reads exactly one client/team/topic doc; enforces isolation + access in code) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.24 Tf 1 0 0 1 56.00 309.01 Tm (GroundingChecker          Flags any answer claim not supported by the retrieved text                  ) Tj ET
