BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 655.88 Tm (  -> ScopedStandardsRetriever\(client=Banking, team=Team_A, topic=security\)) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 645.25 Tm (  -> GroundingChecker verifies the drafted answer against the doc) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 58.00 634.62 Tm (  -> Final response \(text + chat_context + sly_data\) returned to the frontend) Tj ET
